Erlang bindings for ZeroMQ (http://www.zeromq.org).

This is experimental code, expect frequent api/code changes. 

Examples
Following samples require libzmq.so, if zeromq library is not installed 
include libzmq.so path in LD_LIBRARY_PATH.
    PUB/SUB zmq_pubserver/zmq_subclient
    REQ/REP zmq_repserver/zmq_reqclient

Build
Set ERL_INTERFACE_DIR and ZMQ_DIR paths in priv/Makefile.

